s%20library.%20It's%20a%20sequel%2C%20which%20is%20rare%20for%20such%20an%20innovation-focused%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20lack%20of%20innovation%20gives%20the%20Switch%202%20its%20greatest%20strengths%20and%20worst%20flaws.%20On%20the%20one%20hand%2C%20the%20system%20carries%20over%20everything%20I%20loved%20about%20the%20original%20console%2C%20including%20its%20massive%20library%20and%20iconic%20blend%20of%20handheld%20and%20TV%20gaming.%20But%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20it%20offers%20what%20ultimately%20amounts%20to%20a%20similar%20gaming%20experience%20at%20jacked-up%20prices.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20spent%20more%20than%20a%20week%20with%20the%20Nintendo%20Switch%202%2C%20playing%20a%20variety%20of%20games%20every%20day.%20Although%20I%20consider%20it%20a%20no-brainer%20purchase%20for%20players%20who%20never%20bought%20a%20Switch%2C%20I'm%20not%20convinced%20it's%20worth%20upgrading%20from%20the%20original.%20At%20least%2C%20not%20yet.%20I'm%20confident%20the%20Switch%202%20will%20eventually%20become%20an%20even%20better%20console%20than%20the%20Switch%201%2C%20but%20it%20needs%20more%20exclusive%20games%20to%20get%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESee%20also%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fnintendo-switch-2-vs-switch-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_self%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3ENintendo%20Switch%202%20vs.%20Nintendo%20Switch%201%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22effbe75b-7729-4c91-acea-f9dd4d19141d%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Design%20and%20features%5C%22%3EThe%20Nintendo%20Switch%202%20looks%20and%20feels%20better%20than%20the%20original%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222800%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20Nintendo%20Switch%20(bottom)%20and%20a%20Nintendo%20Switch%202%20(top)%2C%20sitting%20against%20a%20black%20background%20and%20displaying%20the%20home%20screen.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F684c66743d588