021%2C%20and%20this%20type%20of%20screen%20offers%20higher%20contrast.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20said%2C%20this%20new%20display's%20colors%20are%20still%20noticeably%20more%20vibrant%20than%20the%20standard%20Switch's%20LCD.%20The%20improved%20image%20quality%20is%20in%20part%20due%20to%20the%20screen's%20support%20for%20high%20dynamic%20range%20(HDR)%2C%20a%20feature%20that%20the%20Switch%201%20didn't%20have.%20HDR%20enables%20enhanced%20contrast%20and%20a%20wider%20range%20of%20colors.%20Though%20the%20Switch%202's%20backlight%20isn't%20bright%20or%20precise%20enough%20to%20showcase%20the%20full%20impact%20of%20what%20HDR%20can%20do%2C%20it%20still%20benefits%20from%20this%20feature.%20You%20can%20learn%20more%20in%20our%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fwhat-is-hdr-tv%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHDR%20guide%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20excited%20to%20see%20more%20games%20take%20advantage%20of%20the%20console's%20120Hz%20refresh%20rate%20(up%20from%2060Hz%20on%20the%20original%20Switch)%20and%20the%20dock's%204K%20output%20for%20Ultra%20HD%20gaming%20on%20a%204K%20TV.%20The%20higher%20refresh%20rate%20can%20provide%20smoother%20motion%2C%20while%20the%20higher%20resolution%20offers%20a%20sharper%2C%20more%20detailed%20picture.%20There's%20only%20one%20game%20released%20so%20far%20that%20goes%20up%20to%20120%20FPS%2C%20the%20%26quot%3BNintendo%20Switch%202%20Welcome%20Tour%26quot%3B%20tech%20demo%2C%20and%20it%20does%20indeed%20look%20very%20smooth.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222520%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Nintendo%20Switch%202's%20left%20Joy-Con%20controller%20being%20used%20as%20a%20mouse.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F684c6a473d5881a51c1b6844%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221890%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20look%20at%20a%20Switch%202%20Joy-Con%20controller%20being%20used%20like%20a%20mouse.%3Cp%3EWilliam%20Antonelli%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2