erience%2C%20even%20though%20I%20loved%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2257609e5c-1255-453c-81e8-424879966863%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20was%20hesitant%20about%20going%20to%20sleepaway%20camp%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20I%20counted%20the%20days%20until%20my%20departure%2C%20I%20started%20to%20worry.%20I%20am%20shy%20by%20nature%20and%20worried%20about%20making%20friends.%20I%20worried%20about%20how%20I%20would%20sleep%20in%20a%20room%20full%20of%20girls%20and%20whether%20I%20would%20like%20the%20food.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20thought%20a%20bad%20counselor%20could%20ruin%20my%20summer%20and%20hoped%20for%20someone%20more%20like%20a%20cool%20older%20sister%20to%20hang%20out%20with%20rather%20than%20a%20teacher%20hell-bent%20on%20keeping%20campers%20in%20line.%20Desperate%20to%20fit%20in%2C%20I%20hoped%20I%20had%20packed%20the%20right%20kinds%20of%20clothes%20and%20a%20swimsuit.%20Although%20I%20wouldn't%20have%20admitted%20it%20then%2C%20I%20was%20worried%20about%20missing%20my%20family%20and%20being%20homesick.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f5e571d6-ceaa-44d2-a367-1a7758cff93f%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20loved%20every%20minute%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20an%20uncertain%20first%20few%20days%2C%20I%20settled%20into%20overnight%20camp.%20I%20swam%20with%20friends%2C%20played%20volleyball%20with%20my%20counselor%2C%20and%20got%20a%20lead%20role%20in%20the%20end-of-camp%20show.%20We%20ran%20feral%20through%20the%20mountains%20and%20woods%2C%20playing%20capture%20the%20flag%20and%20enjoying%20being%20surrounded%20by%20the%20majesty%20of%20tall%20trees%20and%20chirping%20birds%20-%20a%20far%20cry%20from%20the%20endless%20concrete%20and%20loud%20sounds%20of%20the%20city%20where%20most%20of%20us%20lived.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENights%20were%20magical.%20After%20the%20sun%20went%20down%2C%20we%20huddled%20around%20a%20campfire%2C%20singing%20camp%20songs%20and%20telling%20ghost%20stories%20that%20got%20progressively%20scarier%20until%20one%20of%20the%20girls%