r%20a%20substantial%20part%20of%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20she%20gets%20a%20bit%20of%20Cillian%20at%20the%20end.%20All%20I%20can%20say%20is%20you%20have%20to%20wait%20for%20Cillian%2C%20but%20hopefully%20he%20will%20help%20us%20get%20the%20third%20film%20financed.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESo%20where%20are%20things%20with%20the%20third%20movie%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20still%20need%20the%20money.%20I%20mean%2C%20we'll%20see%20how%20we%20do%20with%20%26quot%3B28%20Years%20Later.%26quot%3B%20It's%20so%20close%20to%20release%20that%20nobody%20wants%20to%20say%20anything%3B%20they%20just%20don't%20know%20what%20it's%20going%20to%20do.%20And%20I%20respect%20that.%20It's%20a%20lot%20of%20money%2C%20so%20we'll%20see.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIf%20there%20is%20a%20third%20movie%2C%20would%20you%20want%20to%20direct%20it%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOh%2C%20yes.%20That's%20the%20idea.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EYou%20famously%20walked%20off%20the%20last%20James%20Bond%20movie.%20Would%20you%20ever%20give%20Bond%20another%20try%20now%20that%20the%20regime%20has%20changed%20and%20Amazon%20is%20fully%20controlling%20it%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20ship%20has%20sailed.%20The%20thing%20I%20regret%20about%20that%20is%20the%20script%20was%20really%20good.%20John%20Hodge%20is%20a%20wonderful%20writer%2C%20and%20I%20don't%20think%20they%20appreciated%20how%20good%20that%20script%20was%2C%20and%20because%20they%20didn't%2C%20we%20moved%20on%2C%20and%20that's%20the%20way%20it%20should%20be.%20Whatever%20happens%20with%20Bond%20going%20forward%20now%20is%20what%20it%20will%20be.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221284%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Himesh%20Patel%20walking%20across%20a%20street%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68484bd7f748d8c055f361fa%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22856%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EHimesh%20Patel%20in%20%26quot%3BYesterday.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3EUniversal%3C