20unWOOD%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Dr%20Babu.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20heart%20of%20it%20is%20something%20called%20Macro%20Molecular%20Fibre%20Matrix%20(MMFM)%20%E2%80%94%20sounds%20technical%2C%20but%20it%E2%80%99s%20actually%20pretty%20cool.%20Imagine%20you%E2%80%99re%20cleaning%20up%20after%20a%20party%20%E2%80%94%20there%E2%80%99s%20a%20mix%20of%20plastic%20wrappers%2C%20broken%20cutlery%2C%20and%20food%20containers.%20Normally%2C%20you%E2%80%99d%20need%20to%20sort%20each%20type%20of%20plastic%2C%20wash%20everything%20thoroughly%2C%20and%20then%20send%20it%20off%20to%20be%20melted%20at%20high%20temperatures.%20It%E2%80%99s%20messy%2C%20energy-heavy%2C%20and%20most%20of%20the%20time%2C%20a%20lot%20of%20that%20plastic%20just%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F295373%2Feconiture-turns-plastic-waste-into-sustainable-furniture-video%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eends%20up%20in%20the%20trash%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-06-11T170107.402-1749641498.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22creating%20the%20material%20called%20unWOOD%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-06-11T170107.402-1749641498.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-06-11T170107.402-1749641498-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-06-11T170107.402-1749641498-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-06-11T170107.402-1749641498-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.c