20found%20a%20unique%20niche.%20%E2%80%9CSteel%20rusts%2C%20cement%20cracks%2C%20wood%20swells%20in%20moisture%2C%20and%20plastic%20breaks%20under%20the%20sun%2C%E2%80%9D%20Vishal%20says.%20%E2%80%9CWe%E2%80%99re%20solving%20all%20of%20that.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJust%2011%20park%20benches%20made%20from%20unWOOD%20save%20one%20fully%20mature%20tree%2C%20and%20repurpose%20about%2014%2C000%20plastic%20bottles%2C%2044%2C000%20snack%20packets%2C%20or%201%2C500%20broken%20toys%20that%20would%20have%20otherwise%20polluted%20the%20planet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20officially%20launching%20as%20a%20company%20in%20April%202025%2C%20unWOOD%20has%20already%20recycled%20over%2010%20metric%20tonnes%20of%20plastic%20waste%20and%20saved%2031%20trees.%20And%20they%E2%80%99re%20just%20getting%20started.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhere%20learning%20meets%20sustainability%3A%20%E2%80%98Benches%20for%20Change%E2%80%99%20initiative%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMillions%20of%20children%20in%20underserved%20Indian%20schools%20study%20seated%20on%20bare%20floors%20%E2%80%94%20a%20reality%20that%20affects%20their%20health%2C%20dignity%2C%20and%20learning.%20unWOOD%20saw%20an%20opportunity%20to%20change%20this.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20wanted%20to%20bring%20comfort%20and%20sustainability%20into%20classrooms%20that%20had%20neither%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Vishal.%20%E2%80%9CThat%E2%80%99s%20how%20our%20%E2%80%98Benches%20for%20Change%E2%80%99%20initiative%20began.%E2%80%9D%20Through%20this%20programme%2C%20unWOOD%20collaborates%20with%20corporates%2C%20non-governmental%20organisations%2C%20and%20philanthropists%20to%20provide%20schools%20with%20sturdy%2C%20sustainable%20benches%20made%20from%20recycled%20plastic.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2F